1 /**
  2  * @class PrivateJainSipMessageConnector
  3  * @private
  4  * @classdesc Private framework class handling  SIP client/user message control 
  5  * @constructor
  6  * @param {PrivateJainSipClientConnector} clientConnector clientConnector owner object
  7  * @param {WebRTCommMessage} webRTCommMessage WebRTCommMessage "connected" object
  8  * @param {string} sipCallId   SIP Call ID
  9  * @throw {String} Exception "bad argument"
 10  * @author Laurent STRULLU (laurent.strullu@orange.com) 
 11  * @author Jean Deruelle (jean.deruelle@Å§elestax.com)
 12  */
 13 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector = function(clientConnector, webRTCommMessage, sipCallId)
 14 {
 15     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:PrivateJainSipMessageConnector()");
 16     if (clientConnector instanceof PrivateJainSipClientConnector && webRTCommMessage instanceof WebRTCommMessage)
 17     {
 18         if (typeof(sipCallId) === 'string')
 19         {
 20             this.sipCallId = sipCallId;
 21         }
 22         else
 23         {
 24             this.sipCallId = new String(new Date().getTime());
 25         }
 26         this.clientConnector = clientConnector;
 27         this.webRTCommMessage = webRTCommMessage;
 28         this.sipMessageState = undefined;
 29     } else {
 30         throw "PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:PrivateJainSipMessageConnector(): bad arguments"
 31     }
 32 };

 34 /**
 35  * SIP Message Control state machine constant
 36  * @private
 37  * @constant
 38  */
 39 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.SIP_MESSAGE_SENDING_STATE = "SIP_MESSAGE_SENDING_STATE";
 40 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.SIP_MESSAGE_407_STATE = "SIP_MESSAGE_407_STATE";
 41 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.SIP_MESSAGE_SENT_STATE = "SIP_MESSAGE_SENT_STATE";
 42 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.SIP_MESSAGE_SEND_FAILED_STATE = "SIP_MESSAGE_SEND_FAILED_STATE";
 43 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.SIP_MESSAGE_RECEIVED_STATE = "SIP_MESSAGE_RECEIVED_STATE";

 46 /**

 51 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.getId= function() {
 52     return this.sipCallId;

 55 /**
 56  * Send Authenticated SIP MESSAGE request
 57  * @param {Request} jainSipMessageRequest 
 58  * @param {AuthorizationHeader} jainSipAuthorizationHeader
 59  * @private
 60  */
 61 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.sendAuthenticatedSipMessageRequest = function(jainSipMessageRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader) {
 62     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:sendAuthenticatedSipMessageRequest()");
 63     jainSipMessageRequest.removeHeader("Authorization");
 64     var newJainSipMessageRequest = new SIPRequest();
 65     newJainSipMessageRequest.setMethod(jainSipMessageRequest.getMethod());
 66     newJainSipMessageRequest.setRequestURI(jainSipMessageRequest.getRequestURI());
 67     var headerList = jainSipMessageRequest.getHeaders();
 68     for (var i = 0; i < headerList.length; i++)
 69     {
 70     	newJainSipMessageRequest.addHeader(headerList[i]);
 71     }
 72 
 73     var num = new Number(jainSipMessageRequest.getCSeq().getSeqNumber());
 74     newJainSipMessageRequest.getCSeq().setSeqNumber(num + 1);
 75     newJainSipMessageRequest.setCallId(jainSipMessageRequest.getCallId());
 76     newJainSipMessageRequest.setVia(this.clientConnector.jainSipListeningPoint.getViaHeader());
 77     newJainSipMessageRequest.setFrom(jainSipMessageRequest.getFrom());
 78     newJainSipMessageRequest.setTo(jainSipMessageRequest.getTo());
 79     newJainSipMessageRequest.setMaxForwards(jainSipMessageRequest.getMaxForwards());
 80     if (jainSipMessageRequest.getContent() !== null)
 81     {
 82         var content = jainSipMessageRequest.getContent();
 83         var contentType = jainSipMessageRequest.getContentTypeHeader();
 84         newJainSipMessageRequest.setContent(content, contentType);
 85     }
 86     
 87     this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(newJainSipMessageRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
 88     jainSipMessageTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(newJainSipMessageRequest);
 89     newJainSipMessageRequest.setTransaction(jainSipMessageTransaction);
 90     jainSipMessageTransaction.sendRequest();
 91 };

 93 /**
 94  * PrivateJainSipClientConnector interface implementation: handle SIP Request event
 95  * @public 
 96  * @param {RequestEvent} requestEvent 
 97  */
 98 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent = function(requestEvent) {
 99     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent() requestEvent : " + requestEvent);
100 
101     this.sipMessageState = this.SIP_MESSAGE_RECEIVED_STATE;
102 
103     // Send SIP 200 OK response   
104     var jainSipRequest = requestEvent.getRequest();
105     var jainSip200OKResponse = jainSipRequest.createResponse(200, "OK");
106     jainSip200OKResponse.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
107     jainSip200OKResponse.removeHeader("P-Asserted-Identity");
108     jainSip200OKResponse.removeHeader("P-Charging-Vector");
109     jainSip200OKResponse.removeHeader("P-Charging-Function-Addresses");
110     jainSip200OKResponse.removeHeader("P-Called-Party-ID");
111     jainSip200OKResponse.removeContent();
112     requestEvent.getServerTransaction().sendResponse(jainSip200OKResponse);
113 
114     this.webRTCommMessage.from = requestEvent.getRequest().getHeader("From").getAddress().getURI().getUser();
115     this.webRTCommMessage.text = requestEvent.getRequest().getContent();
116 
117     if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall)
118     {
119         if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageReceivedEvent)
120         {
121             var that = this;
122             setTimeout(function() {
123                 try {
124                     that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageReceivedEvent(that.webRTCommMessage);
125                 }
126                 catch (exception) {
127                     console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
128                 }
129             }, 1);
130         }
131     }
132     else
133     {
134         // No linked call to the event message, forward the message to the client   
135         if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageReceivedEvent)
136         {
137             var that = this;
138             setTimeout(function() {
139                 try {
140                     that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageReceivedEvent(that.webRTCommMessage);
141                 }
142                 catch (exception) {
143                     console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
144                 }
145             }, 1);
146         }
147     }
148     
149     this.close();
150 };

152 /**
153  * PrivateJainSipClientConnector interface implementation: handle SIP response event
154  * @public 
155  * @param {ResponseEvent} responseEvent 
156  */
157 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent = function(responseEvent) {
158     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent() responseEvent : " + responseEvent.getResponse().getStatusLine().getReasonPhrase());
159     var jainSipResponse = responseEvent.getResponse();
160     var statusCode = parseInt(jainSipResponse.getStatusCode());
161     
162     if (this.sipMessageState === this.SIP_MESSAGE_SENDING_STATE || this.sipMessageState === this.SIP_MESSAGE_407_STATE)
163     {
164         if (statusCode >= 100 && statusCode < 300) {
165             this.sipMessageState = this.SIP_MESSAGE_SENT_STATE;
166             if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall)
167             {
168                 if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSentEvent)
169                 {
170                     var that = this;
171                     setTimeout(function() {
172                         try {
173                             that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSentEvent(that.webRTCommMessage);
174                         }
175                         catch (exception) {
176                             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
177                         }
178                     }, 1);
179                 }
180             }
181             else
182             {            	
183                 // No linked call to the event message, forward the message to the client   
184                 if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSentEvent)
185                 {
186                     var that = this;
187                     setTimeout(function() {
188                         try {
189                             that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSentEvent(that.webRTCommMessage);
190                         }
191                         catch (exception) {
192                             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
193                         }
194                     }, 1);
195                 }
196             }
197         } else {
198             if (statusCode === 407)
199             {
200         	this.sipMessageState = this.SIP_MESSAGE_407_STATE;
201     		
202                 // Send Authenticated SIP INVITE
203         	var jainSipOriginalMessageRequest = responseEvent.getOriginalTransaction().getOriginalRequest();
204                 var jainSipAuthorizationHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createAuthorizationHeader(jainSipResponse, jainSipOriginalMessageRequest, 						   this.clientConnector.configuration.sipPassword, this.clientConnector.configuration.sipLogin);
205                 this.sendAuthenticatedSipMessageRequest(jainSipOriginalMessageRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
206                 return;
207             } else {
208             	this.sipMessageState = this.SIP_MESSAGE_SEND_FAILED_STATE;
209             }
210         	
211             if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall)
212             {
213             	if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent)
214                 {
215                     var that = this;
216                     setTimeout(function() {
217                         try {
218                             that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent(that.webRTCommMessage, jainSipResponse.getStatusLine().getReasonPhrase());
219                         }
220                         catch (exception) {
221                             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
222                         }
223                     }, 1);
224                 }
225             }
226             else
227             {
228             	if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent)
229                 // No linked call to the event message, forward the message to the client                  
230                 {
231                     var that = this;
232                     setTimeout(function() {
233                         try {
234                             that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent(that.webRTCommMessage, jainSipResponse.getStatusLine().getReasonPhrase());
235                         }
236                         catch (exception) {
237                             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
238                         }
239                     }, 1);
240                 }
241             }
242         }
243     }
244     else
245     {
246         console.error("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipResponseEvent() : bad state : " + this.sipMessageState);
247     }    
248     this.close();
249 };

251 /**
252  * PrivateJainSipClientConnector interface implementation: handle SIP timeout event
253  * @public 
254  * @param {TimeoutEvent} timeoutEvent
255  */
256 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.onJainSipClientConnectorSipTimeoutEvent = function(timeoutEvent) {
257     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipTimeoutEvent()");
258 
259     if (this.sipMessageState === this.SIP_MESSAGE_SENDING_STATE)
260     {
261         this.sipMessageState = this.SIP_MESSAGE_SEND_FAILED_STATE;
262         if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall)
263         {
264             if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent)
265             {
266                 var that = this;
267                 setTimeout(function() {
268                     try {
269                         that.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommCall.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent(that.webRTCommMessage, "SIP Timeout");
270                     }
271                     catch (exception) {
272                         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipTimeoutEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
273                     }
274                 }, 1);
275             }
276         }
277         else
278         {
279             // No linked call to the event message, forward the message to the client   
280             if (this.webRTCommMessage.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent)
281             {
282                 var that = this;
283                 setTimeout(function() {
284                     try {
285                         that.webRTCommClient.eventListener.onWebRTCommMessageSendErrorEvent(that.webRTCommMessage, "SIP Timeout");
286                     }
287                     catch (exception) {
288                         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipTimeoutEvent(): catched exception in event listener:" + exception);
289                     }
290                 }, 1);
291             }
292         }
293     }
294     else
295     {
296         console.error("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:onJainSipClientConnectorSipTimeoutEvent() : bad state : " + this.sipMessageState);
297     }
298         
299     this.close();
300 };

302 /**
303  * Asynchronous action : close message connector in each case.
304  * @public 
305  */ 
306 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.close =function(){	
307     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:close(): this.sipCallState="+this.sipMessageState);
308     this.clientConnector.removeSessionConnector(this.sipCallId);		
309 };

312 /**
313  * Send SIP MESSAGE request
314  * @public 
315  */
316 PrivateJainSipMessageConnector.prototype.send = function() {
317     console.debug("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:send()");
318     if (this.sipMessageState === undefined)
319     {
320         var toSipUri = this.webRTCommMessage.to;
321         if (toSipUri.indexOf("@") === -1)
322         {
323             //No domain, add caller one 
324             toSipUri += "@" + this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDomain;
325         }
326         var fromSipUriString = this.clientConnector.configuration.sipUserName + "@" + this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDomain;
327         var jainSipCseqHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createCSeqHeader(1, "MESSAGE");
328         var jainSipCallIdHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createCallIdHeader(this.sipCallId);
329         var jainSipMaxForwardHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createMaxForwardsHeader(70);
330         var jainSipRequestUri = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, toSipUri);
331         var jainSipAllowListHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createHeaders("Allow: INVITE,ACK,CANCEL,BYE,MESSAGE");
332         var jainSipFromUri = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, fromSipUriString);
333         var jainSipFromAdress = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createAddress_name_uri(this.clientConnector.configuration.displayName, jainSipFromUri);
334 
335         // Setup display name
336         if (this.clientConnector.configuration.displayName)
337         {
338             jainSipFromAdress.setDisplayName(this.clientConnector.configuration.displayName);
339         }
340         else if (this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDisplayName)
341         {
342             jainSipFromAdress.setDisplayName(this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDisplayName);
343         }
344         var tagFrom = new Date().getTime();
345         var jainSipFromHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createFromHeader(jainSipFromAdress, tagFrom);
346         var jainSiptoUri = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, toSipUri);
347         var jainSipToAddress = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createAddress_name_uri(null, jainSiptoUri);
348         var jainSipToHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createToHeader(jainSipToAddress, null);
349         var jainSipViaHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipListeningPoint.getViaHeader();
350         var jainSipContentTypeHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createContentTypeHeader("text", "plain");
351 
352         this.jainSipMessageRequest = this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.createRequest(
353                 jainSipRequestUri,
354                 "MESSAGE",
355                 jainSipCallIdHeader,
356                 jainSipCseqHeader,
357                 jainSipFromHeader,
358                 jainSipToHeader,
359                 jainSipViaHeader,
360                 jainSipMaxForwardHeader,
361                 jainSipContentTypeHeader,
362                 this.webRTCommMessage.text);
363 
364         this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipMessageRequest, jainSipAllowListHeader);
365         this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipMessageRequest, this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
366         var jainSipTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(this.jainSipMessageRequest);
367         this.jainSipMessageRequest.setTransaction(jainSipTransaction);
368         jainSipTransaction.sendRequest();
369         this.sipMessageState = this.SIP_MESSAGE_SENDING_STATE;
370     }
371     else
372     {
373         console.error("PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:send(): bad state, unauthorized action");
374         throw "PrivateJainSipMessageConnector:send(): bad state, unauthorized action";
375     }
376 };

415 /**
416  * @class PrivateJainSipCallConnector
417  * @private
418  * @classdesc Private framework class handling  SIP client/user call control: ringing, ringing back, accept, reject, cancel, bye 
419  * @constructor
420  * @param {PrivateJainSipClientConnector} clientConnector clientConnector owner object
421  * @param {WebRTCommCall} webRTCommCall WebRTCommCall "connected" object
422  * @param {string} sipCallId   SIP Call ID
423  * @throw {String} Exception "bad argument"
424  * @author Laurent STRULLU (laurent.strullu@orange.com) 
425  */
426 PrivateJainSipCallConnector = function(clientConnector, webRTCommCall, sipCallId)
427 {
428     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:PrivateJainSipCallConnector()");
429     if (clientConnector instanceof PrivateJainSipClientConnector && webRTCommCall instanceof WebRTCommCall)
430     {
431         if (typeof(sipCallId) === 'string')
432         {
433             this.sipCallId = sipCallId;
434         }
435         else
436         {
437             this.sipCallId = new String(new Date().getTime());
438         }
439         this.clientConnector = clientConnector;
440         this.webRTCommCall = webRTCommCall;
441         this.webRTCommCall.id = this.sipCallId;
442         this.configuration = undefined;
443         this.resetSipContext();
444     }
445     else
446     {
447         throw "PrivateJainSipCallConnector:PrivateJainSipCallConnector(): bad arguments"
448     }
449 };

474 /**
475  * Get SIP communication opened/closed status 
476  * @public
477  * @returns {boolean} true if opened, false if closed
478  */
479 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.isOpened = function() {
480     return ((this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_ACCEPTED_STATE) || (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_ACCEPTED_STATE));
481 };

492 /**
493  * Open JAIN SIP call/communication, asynchronous action,  opened or error event is notified to WebRtcClientCall eventListener
494  * @public 
495  * @param {object} configuration  WebRTC communication configuration 
496  * <p> Communication configuration sample: <br>
497  * { <br>
498  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">displayName:alice,<br></span>
499  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">localMediaStream: [LocalMediaStream],<br></span>
500  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">audioMediaFlag:true,<br></span>
501  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">videoMediaFlag:false,<br></span>
502  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">dataMediaFlag:false,<br></span>
503  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">audioCodecsFilter:PCMA,PCMU,OPUS,<br></span>
504  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">videoCodecsFilter:VP8,H264,<br></span>
505  * }<br>
506  * </p>
507  * @public  
508  * @throw {String} Exception "bad configuration, missing parameter"
509  * @throw {String} Exception "bad state, unauthorized action"
510  */
511 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.open = function(configuration) {
512     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:open()");
513     if (this.sipCallState === undefined)
514     {
515         if (typeof(configuration) === 'object')
516         {
517             // Calling
518             if (this.checkConfiguration(configuration) === true)
519             {
520                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_INITIAL_STATE;
521                 this.configuration = configuration;
522             }
523             else
524             {
525                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:open(): bad configuration");
526                 throw "PrivateJainSipCallConnector:open(): bad configuration";
527             }
528         }
529         else
530         {
531             // Called
532             this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITED_INITIAL_STATE;
533         }
534     }
535     else
536     {
537         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:open(): bad state, unauthorized action");
538         throw "PrivateJainSipCallConnector:open(): bad state, unauthorized action";
539     }
540 };
541 
542 /**
543  * Close JAIN SIP communication, asynchronous action, closed event are notified to the WebRTCommClient eventListener
544  * @public 
545  * @throw {String} Exception "bad state, unauthorized action"
546  * @throw {String} Exception "internal error,check console logs"
547  */
548 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.close = function() {
549     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:close(): this.sipCallState=" + this.sipCallState);
550     if (this.sipCallState !== undefined)
551     {
552         try
553         {
554             if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INITIAL_INVITING_STATE)
555             {
556                 // SIP INVITE has not been sent yet.
557                 this.resetSipContext();
558                 this.clientConnector.removeSessionConnector(this.sipCallId);
559                 // Notify closed event
560                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallClosedEvent();
561             }
562             else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_STATE || this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_407_STATE)
563             {
564                 // SIP INIVTE has been sent, need to cancel it
565                 this.jainSipInvitingCancelRequest = this.jainSipInvitingTransaction.createCancel();
566                 this.jainSipInvitingCancelRequest.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
567                 this.jainSipInvitingCancelTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(this.jainSipInvitingCancelRequest);
568                 this.jainSipInvitingCancelTransaction.sendRequest();
569                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_CANCELLING_STATE;
570             }
571             else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_ACCEPTED_STATE)
572             {
573                 // Sent SIP BYE
574                 var jainSipByeRequest = this.jainSipInvitingDialog.createRequest("BYE");
575                 jainSipByeRequest.removeHeader("Contact");
576                 jainSipByeRequest.removeHeader("User-Agent");
577                 jainSipByeRequest.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
578                 var clientTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(jainSipByeRequest);
579                 this.jainSipInvitingDialog.sendRequest(clientTransaction);
580                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_STATE;
581                 // Notify closed event
582                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallClosedEvent();
583             }
584             else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_INITIAL_STATE)
585             {
586                 // Rejected  480 Temporarily Unavailable
587                 var jainSipResponse480 = this.jainSipInvitedRequest.createResponse(480, "Temporarily Unavailable");
588                 jainSipResponse480.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
589                 this.jainSipInvitedTransaction.sendResponse(jainSipResponse480);
590                 this.resetSipContext();
591                 this.clientConnector.removeSessionConnector(this.sipCallId);
592             }
593             else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_ACCEPTED_STATE)
594             {
595                 // Sent SIP BYE
596                 var jainSipByeRequest = this.jainSipInvitedDialog.createRequest("BYE");
597                 jainSipByeRequest.removeHeader("Contact");
598                 jainSipByeRequest.removeHeader("User-Agent");
599                 jainSipByeRequest.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
600                 var clientTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(jainSipByeRequest);
601                 this.jainSipInvitedDialog.sendRequest(clientTransaction);
602                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITED_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_STATE;
603             }
604             else
605             {
606                 this.resetSipContext();
607                 this.clientConnector.removeSessionConnector(this.sipCallId);
608                 // Notify closed event
609                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallClosedEvent();
610             }
611         }
612         catch (exception)
613         {
614             console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:close(): catched exception:" + exception);
615             this.resetSipContext();
616             this.clientConnector.removeSessionConnector(this.sipCallId);
617             // Notify closed event
618             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallClosedEvent();
619         }
620     }
621 };

625  * @public

629 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.reject = function() {

633         try
634         {

640         catch (exception)
641         {
642             console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:reject(): catched exception:" + exception);
643         }
644         this.close();
645     }
646     else
647     {
648         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:reject(): bad state, unauthorized action");
649         throw "PrivateJainSipCallConnector:reject(): bad state, unauthorized action";
650     }

756 /**
757  * Handle SIP request event for inviting call
758  * @private 
759  * @param {RequestEvent} requestEvent 
760  */
761 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.processInvitingSipRequestEvent = function(requestEvent) {
762     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): this.sipCallState=" + this.sipCallState);
763     var jainSipRequest = requestEvent.getRequest();
764     var requestMethod = jainSipRequest.getMethod();
765     if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_INITIAL_STATE)
766     {
767         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
768     }
769     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_STATE)
770     {
771         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
772     }
773     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_407_STATE)
774     {
775         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
776     }
777     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_ERROR_STATE)
778     {
779         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
780     }
781     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_ACCEPTED_STATE)
782     {
783         if (requestMethod === "BYE")
784         {
785             try
786             {
787                 // Sent 200 OK BYE
788                 var jainSip200OKResponse = jainSipRequest.createResponse(200, "OK");
789                 jainSip200OKResponse.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
790                 requestEvent.getServerTransaction().sendResponse(jainSip200OKResponse);
791                 // Update SIP call state
792                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_HANGUP_STATE;
793             }
794             catch (exception)
795             {
796                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): catched exception exception:" + exception);
797             }
798 
799             // Notify the hangup event
800             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallHangupEvent();
801 
802             // Close the call
803             this.close();
804         }
805         else
806         {
807             console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
808         }
809     }
810     else
811     {
812         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
813     }
814 };
815 
816 /**
817  * Send SIP INVITE request
818  * @private 
819  */
820 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.sendSipInviteRequest = function() {
821     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:sendSipInviteRequest()");
822     // Send INVITE 
823     var calleeSipUri = this.webRTCommCall.getCalleePhoneNumber();
824     if (calleeSipUri.indexOf("@") === -1)
825     {
826         //No domain, add caller one 
827         calleeSipUri += "@" + this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDomain;
828     }
829     var fromSipUriString = this.clientConnector.configuration.sipUserName + "@" + this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDomain;
830     var jainSipCseqHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createCSeqHeader(1, "INVITE");
831     var jainSipCallIdHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createCallIdHeader(this.sipCallId);
832     var jainSipMaxForwardHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createMaxForwardsHeader(70);
833     var jainSipRequestUri = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, calleeSipUri);
834     var jainSipAllowListHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createHeaders("Allow: INVITE,ACK,CANCEL,BYE");
835     var jainSipFromUri = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, fromSipUriString);
836     var jainSipFromAdress = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createAddress_name_uri(this.configuration.displayName, jainSipFromUri);
837     // Setup display name
838     if (this.configuration.displayName)
839     {
840         jainSipFromAdress.setDisplayName(this.configuration.displayName);
841     }
842     else if (this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDisplayName)
843     {
844         jainSipFromAdress.setDisplayName(this.clientConnector.configuration.sipDisplayName);
845     }
846     var tagFrom = new Date().getTime();
847     var jainSipFromHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createFromHeader(jainSipFromAdress, tagFrom);
848     var jainSiptoUri = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, calleeSipUri);
849     var jainSipToAddress = this.clientConnector.jainSipAddressFactory.createAddress_name_uri(null, jainSiptoUri);
850     var jainSipToHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createToHeader(jainSipToAddress, null);
851     var jainSipViaHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipListeningPoint.getViaHeader();
852     var jainSipContentTypeHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createContentTypeHeader("application", "sdp");
853     this.jainSipInvitingRequest = this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.createRequest(jainSipRequestUri, "INVITE",
854             jainSipCallIdHeader,
855             jainSipCseqHeader,
856             jainSipFromHeader,
857             jainSipToHeader,
858             jainSipViaHeader,
859             jainSipMaxForwardHeader,
860             jainSipContentTypeHeader,
861             this.sdpOffer);
862 
863     this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipInvitingRequest, jainSipAllowListHeader);
864     this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipInvitingRequest, this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
865     this.jainSipInvitingTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(this.jainSipInvitingRequest);
866     this.jainSipInvitingRequest.setTransaction(this.jainSipInvitingTransaction);
867     this.jainSipInvitingDialog = this.jainSipInvitingTransaction.getDialog();
868     this.jainSipInvitingTransaction.sendRequest();
869 };
870 
871 /**
872  * Send SIP INVITE request
873  * @private 
874  * @param {AuthorizationHeader} jainSipAuthorizationHeader Authorization Header
875  */
876 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.sendAuthenticatedSipInviteRequest = function(jainSipAuthorizationHeader) {
877     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:sendAuthenticatedSipInviteRequest()");
878     this.jainSipInvitingRequest.removeHeader("Authorization");
879     var newJainSipInvitingRequest = new SIPRequest();
880     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setMethod(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getMethod());
881     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setRequestURI(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getRequestURI());
882     var headerList = this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getHeaders();
883     for (var i = 0; i < headerList.length; i++)
884     {
885         newJainSipInvitingRequest.addHeader(headerList[i]);
886     }
887 
888     var num = new Number(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getCSeq().getSeqNumber());
889     newJainSipInvitingRequest.getCSeq().setSeqNumber(num + 1);
890     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setCallId(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getCallId());
891     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setVia(this.clientConnector.jainSipListeningPoint.getViaHeader());
892     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setFrom(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getFrom());
893     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setTo(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getTo());
894     newJainSipInvitingRequest.setMaxForwards(this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getMaxForwards());
895 
896     if (this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getContent() !== null)
897     {
898         var content = this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getContent();
899         var contentType = this.jainSipInvitingRequest.getContentTypeHeader();
900         newJainSipInvitingRequest.setContent(content, contentType);
901     }
902     this.jainSipInvitingRequest = newJainSipInvitingRequest;
903     this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipInvitingRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
904     this.jainSipInvitingTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(this.jainSipInvitingRequest);
905     this.jainSipInvitingRequest.setTransaction(this.jainSipInvitingransaction);
906     this.jainSipInvitingTransaction.sendRequest();
907 };

909 /**
910  * Handle SIP response event for inviting call
911  * @private 
912  * @param {ResponseEvent} responseEvent 
913  */
914 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.processInvitingSipResponseEvent = function(responseEvent) {
915     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipResponseEvent(): this.sipCallState=" + this.sipCallState);
916     var jainSipResponse = responseEvent.getResponse();
917     var statusCode = parseInt(jainSipResponse.getStatusCode());
918     if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_STATE)
919     {
920         if (statusCode < 200)
921         {
922             if (statusCode === 180)
923             {
924                 // Notify the ringing back event
925                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallRingingBackEvent();
926             }
927             else if (statusCode === 183)
928             {
929                 // Notify asynchronously the in progress event
930                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallInProgressEvent();
931             }
932             console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipResponseEvent(): 1XX response ignored");
933         }
934         else if (statusCode === 407)
935         {
936             // Send Authenticated SIP INVITE
937             var jainSipAuthorizationHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createAuthorizationHeader(jainSipResponse, this.jainSipInvitingRequest, this.clientConnector.configuration.sipPassword, this.clientConnector.configuration.sipLogin);
938             this.sendAuthenticatedSipInviteRequest(jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
939             // Update SIP call state            
940             this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_407_STATE;
941         }
942         else if (statusCode === 200)
943         {
944             this.jainSipInvitingDialog = responseEvent.getOriginalTransaction().getDialog();
945             try
946             {
947                 // Send SIP 200 OK ACK
948                 this.jainSipInvitingDialog.setRemoteTarget(jainSipResponse.getHeader("Contact"));
949                 var jainSipMessageACK = this.jainSipInvitingTransaction.createAck();
950                 jainSipMessageACK.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
951                 this.jainSipInvitingDialog.sendAck(jainSipMessageACK);
952                 // Update SIP call state    
953                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_ACCEPTED_STATE;
954             }
955             catch (exception)
956             {
957                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
958             }
959 
960             try
961             {
962                 var sdpAnswerString = jainSipResponse.getContent();
963                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorRemoteSdpAnswerEvent(sdpAnswerString);
964             }
965             catch (exception)
966             {
967                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
968 
969                 // Notify the error event
970                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallOpenErrorEvent(exception);
971 
972                 // Close the call
973                 this.close();
974             }
975         }
976         else
977         {
978             console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): SIP INVITE failed:" + jainSipResponse.getStatusCode() + "  " + jainSipResponse.getStatusLine().toString());
979             // Update SIP call state    
980             this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_ERROR_STATE;
981             // Notify asynchronously the error event
982             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallOpenErrorEvent(jainSipResponse.getStatusLine().getReasonPhrase());
983 
984             this.close();
985         }
986     }
987     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_CANCELLING_STATE)
988     {
989         // Update SIP call state    
990         this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_CANCELLED_STATE;
991         this.close();
992     }
993     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_407_STATE)
994     {
995         if (statusCode < 200)
996         {
997             console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipResponseEvent(): 1XX response ignored");
998         }
999         else if (statusCode === 200)
1000         {
1001             this.jainSipInvitingDialog = responseEvent.getOriginalTransaction().getDialog();
1002 
1003             try
1004             {
1005                 // Send SIP 200 OK ACK
1006                 this.jainSipInvitingDialog.setRemoteTarget(jainSipResponse.getHeader("Contact"));
1007                 var jainSipMessageACK = this.jainSipInvitingTransaction.createAck();
1008                 jainSipMessageACK.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
1009                 this.jainSipInvitingDialog.sendAck(jainSipMessageACK);
1010                 // Update SIP call state
1011                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_ACCEPTED_STATE;
1012             }
1013             catch (exception)
1014             {
1015                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
1016             }
1017 
1018 
1019             try
1020             {
1021                 var sdpAnswerString = jainSipResponse.getContent();
1022                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorRemoteSdpAnswerEvent(sdpAnswerString);
1023             }
1024             catch (exception)
1025             {
1026                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
1027 
1028                 // Notify the error event
1029                 this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallOpenErrorEvent(exception);
1030 
1031                 // Close the call
1032                 this.close();
1033             }
1034         }
1035         else
1036         {
1037             // Update SIP call state
1038             this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_ERROR_STATE;
1039 
1040             // Notify the error event
1041             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallOpenErrorEvent(jainSipResponse.getStatusLine().getReasonPhrase());
1042 
1043             // Close the call
1044             this.close();
1045         }
1046     }
1047     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_ERROR_STATE)
1048     {
1049         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipResponseEvent(): bad state, SIP response ignored");
1050     }
1051     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_ACCEPTED_STATE)
1052     {
1053         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipResponseEvent(): bad state, SIP response ignored");
1054     }
1055     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_STATE)
1056     {
1057         if (statusCode === 407)
1058         {
1059             try
1060             {
1061                 // Send Authenticated BYE request
1062                 var jainSipByeRequest = this.jainSipInvitingDialog.createRequest("BYE");
1063                 var clientTransaction = this.clientConnector.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(jainSipByeRequest);
1064                 var jainSipAuthorizationHeader = this.clientConnector.jainSipHeaderFactory.createAuthorizationHeader(jainSipResponse, jainSipByeRequest, this.clientConnector.configuration.sipPassword, this.clientConnector.configuration.sipLogin);
1065                 this.clientConnector.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(jainSipByeRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
1066                 this.jainSipInvitingDialog.sendRequest(clientTransaction);
1067                 // Update SIP call state
1068                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITING_HANGINGUP_407_STATE;
1069             }
1070             catch (exception)
1071             {
1072                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
1073                 this.close();
1074             }
1075         }
1076         else
1077         {
1078             // Force close
1079             this.close();
1080         }
1081     }
1082     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITING_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_407_STATE)
1083     {
1084         // Force close
1085         this.close();
1086     }
1087     else
1088     {
1089         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitingSipResponseEvent(): bad state, SIP response ignored");
1090     }
1091 };

1093 /**
1094  * Handle SIP request event for invited call
1095  * @private 
1096  * @param {RequestEvent} requestEvent request event
1097  */
1098 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.processInvitedSipRequestEvent = function(requestEvent) {
1099     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): this.sipCallState=" + this.sipCallState);
1100     var jainSipRequest = requestEvent.getRequest();
1101     var requestMethod = jainSipRequest.getMethod();
1102     var headerFrom = jainSipRequest.getHeader("From");
1103     if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_INITIAL_STATE)
1104     {
1105         if (requestMethod === "INVITE")
1106         {
1107             try
1108             {
1109                 // Store SIP context
1110                 this.jainSipInvitedRequest = jainSipRequest;
1111                 this.jainSipInvitedTransaction = requestEvent.getServerTransaction();
1112                 this.jainSipInvitedDialog = requestEvent.getServerTransaction().getDialog();
1113 
1114                 // Ringing
1115                 var jainSip180ORingingResponse = jainSipRequest.createResponse(180, "Ringing");
1116                 jainSip180ORingingResponse.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
1117                 requestEvent.getServerTransaction().sendResponse(jainSip180ORingingResponse);
1118             }
1119             catch (exception)
1120             {
1121                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
1122             }
1123 
1124             //  Notify remote SDP offer to WebRTCommCall
1125             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorRemoteSdpOfferEvent(this.jainSipInvitedRequest.getContent());
1126 
1127             // Notify incoming communication
1128             var callerPhoneNumber = headerFrom.getAddress().getURI().getUser();
1129             var callerDisplayName = headerFrom.getAddress().getDisplayName();
1130             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallRingingEvent(callerPhoneNumber, callerDisplayName);
1131         }
1132         else if (requestMethod === "CANCEL")
1133         {
1134             try
1135             {
1136                 // Send 200OK CANCEL
1137                 var jainSip200OKResponse = jainSipRequest.createResponse(200, "OK");
1138                 jainSip200OKResponse.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
1139                 requestEvent.getServerTransaction().sendResponse(jainSip200OKResponse);
1140 
1141                 // Send 487 (Request Cancelled) for the INVITE
1142                 var jainSipResponse487 = this.jainSipInvitedRequest.createResponse(487, "(Request Cancelled)");
1143                 this.jainSipInvitedTransaction.sendMessage(jainSipResponse487);
1144 
1145                 // Update SIP call state
1146                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITED_CANCELLED_STATE;
1147             }
1148             catch (exception)
1149             {
1150                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
1151             }
1152 
1153             // Notify asynchronously the hangup event
1154             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallHangupEvent();
1155 
1156             // Close the call
1157             this.close();
1158         }
1159         else
1160         {
1161             console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
1162         }
1163     }
1164     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_ACCEPTED_STATE)
1165     {
1166         if (requestMethod === "BYE")
1167         {
1168             try
1169             {
1170                 // Send 200OK
1171                 var jainSip200OKResponse = jainSipRequest.createResponse(200, "OK");
1172                 jainSip200OKResponse.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
1173                 requestEvent.getServerTransaction().sendResponse(jainSip200OKResponse);
1174 
1175                 // Update SIP call state
1176                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITED_HANGUP_STATE;
1177             }
1178             catch (exception)
1179             {
1180                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): catched exception exception:" + exception);
1181             }
1182 
1183             // Notify asynchronously the hangup event
1184             this.webRTCommCall.onPrivateCallConnectorCallHangupEvent();
1185 
1186             // Close the call
1187             this.close();
1188         }
1189         else if (requestMethod === "ACK")
1190         {
1191             this.jainSipInvitedDialog = requestEvent.getServerTransaction().getDialog();
1192         }
1193         else
1194         {
1195             console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
1196         }
1197     }
1198     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_STATE)
1199     {
1200         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
1201     }
1202     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_407_STATE)
1203     {
1204         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipRequestEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
1205     }
1206 };

1210  * @private

1213 PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.processInvitedSipResponseEvent = function(responseEvent) {
1214     console.debug("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipResponseEvent(): this.invitingState=" + this.invitingState);
1215     var jainSipResponse = responseEvent.getResponse();

1217     if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_STATE)
1218     {

1222     {

1224     }
1225     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_STATE)
1226     {
1227         if (statusCode === 407)
1228         {
1229             try
1230             {
1231                 // Send Authenticated BYE request

1233                 var clientTransaction = this.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(jainSipByeRequest);
1234                 var jainSipAuthorizationHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createAuthorizationHeader(jainSipResponse, jainSipByeRequest, this.configuration.sipPassword, this.configuration.sipLogin);
1235                 this.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(jainSipByeRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
1236                 jainSipByeRequest.addHeader(this.clientConnector.jainSipContactHeader);
1237                 this.jainSipInvitedDialog.sendRequest(clientTransaction);
1238 
1239                 // Update SIP call state
1240                 this.sipCallState = this.SIP_INVITED_HANGINGUP_407_STATE;
1241             }
1242             catch (exception)
1243             {
1244                 console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipResponseEvent(): catched exception, exception:" + exception);
1245                 this.close();
1246             }
1247         }
1248         else
1249         {
1250             this.close();
1251         }
1252     }
1253     else if (this.sipCallState === this.SIP_INVITED_LOCAL_HANGINGUP_407_STATE)
1254     {
1255         // Force close
1256         this.close();
1257     }
1258     else
1259     {
1260         console.error("PrivateJainSipCallConnector:processInvitedSipResponseEvent(): bad state, SIP request ignored");
1261     }
1262 };

1316 /**
1317  * Open SIP client/user agent, asynchronous action, opened or error event is notified to WebRtcClientComm
1318  * @public 
1319  * @param {object} configuration   SIP client/user agent configuration <br>
1320  * <p> Client configuration sample: <br>
1321  * { <br>
1322  * <span style="margin-left: 60px">sipUriContactParameters:undefined,<br></span>
1323  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserAgent:"WebRtcCommTestWebApp/0.0.1",<br></span>
1324  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserAgentCapabilities:"+g.oma.sip-im",<br></span>
1325  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipOutboundProxy:"ws://localhost:5082",<br></span>
1326  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipDomain:"sip.net",<br></span>
1327  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserName:"alice",<br></span>
1328  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipLogin:"alice@sip.net,<br></span>
1329  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipPassword:"1234567890",<br></span>
1330  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipRegisterMode:true,<br></span>
1331  * }<br>
1332  *  </p>
1333  * @throw {String} Exception "bad argument"
1334  * @throw {String} Exception "bad configuration, missing parameter"
1335  * @throw {String} Exception "bad state, unauthorized action"
1336  * @throw {String} Exception [internal error]
1337  */
1338 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.open = function(configuration) {
1339     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open()");
1340     try
1341     {
1342         if (typeof(configuration) === 'object')
1343         {
1344             if (this.openedFlag === false)
1345             {
1346                 if (this.checkConfiguration(configuration) === true)
1347                 {
1348                     this.configuration = configuration;
1349 
1350                     // Create JAIN SIP main objects
1351                     this.jainSipFactory = new SipFactory();
1352                     this.jainSipStack = this.jainSipFactory.createSipStack(this.configuration.sipUserAgent);
1353                     this.jainSipListeningPoint = this.jainSipStack.createListeningPoint(this.configuration.sipOutboundProxy);
1354                     this.jainSipProvider = this.jainSipStack.createSipProvider(this.jainSipListeningPoint);
1355                     this.jainSipProvider.addSipListener(this);
1356                     this.jainSipHeaderFactory = this.jainSipFactory.createHeaderFactory();
1357                     this.jainSipAddressFactory = this.jainSipFactory.createAddressFactory();
1358                     this.jainSipMessageFactory = this.jainSipFactory.createMessageFactory();
1359                     this.jainSipContactHeader = this.jainSipListeningPoint.createContactHeader(this.configuration.sipUserName);
1360                     if (this.configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities)
1361                     {
1362                         this.jainSipContactHeader.setParameter(this.configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities, null);
1363                     }
1364                     if (this.configuration.sipUriContactParameters)
1365                     {
1366                         try
1367                         {
1368                             var sipUri = this.jainSipContactHeader.getAddress().getURI();
1369                             var parameters = this.configuration.sipUriContactParameters.split(";");
1370                             for (var i = 0; i < parameters.length; i++)
1371                             {
1372                                 var nameValue = parameters[i].split("=");
1373                                 sipUri.uriParms.set_nv(new NameValue(nameValue[0], nameValue[1]));
1374                             }
1375                         }
1376                         catch (exception)
1377                         {
1378                             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): catched exception:" + exception);
1379                         }
1380                     }
1381 
1382                     this.jainSipMessageFactory.setDefaultUserAgentHeader(this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createUserAgentHeader(this.jainSipStack.getUserAgent()));
1383                     this.jainSipStack.start();
1384                 }
1385                 else
1386                 {
1387                     console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): bad configuration");
1388                     throw "PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): bad configuration";
1389                 }
1390             }
1391             else
1392             {
1393                 console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): bad state, unauthorized action");
1394                 throw "PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): bad state, unauthorized action";
1395             }
1396         }
1397         else
1398         {
1399             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): bad argument, check API documentation");
1400             throw "PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): bad argument, check API documentation"
1401         }
1402     }
1403     catch (exception) {
1404         this.reset();
1405         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:open(): catched exception:" + exception);
1406         throw exception;
1407     }
1408 };

1410 /**
1411  * Close SIP client/User Agent, asynchronous action,closed event is notified to WebRtcClientComm
1412  * Open SIP Call/communication are closed
1413  * @public 
1414  * @throw {String} Exception "bad state, unauthorized action"
1415  * @throw {String} Exception [internal error]
1416  */
1417 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.close = function() {
1418     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:close()");
1419     try
1420     {
1421         if (this.openedFlag === true)
1422         {
1423             //Force close of open SIP communication
1424             for (var sipSessionId in this.sessionConnectors) {
1425 
1426                 var sessionConnector = this.sessionConnectors[sipSessionId];
1427                 if (sessionConnector instanceof PrivateJainSipCallConnector)
1428                 {
1429                     if (sessionConnector.isOpened())
1430                     {
1431                         sessionConnector.close();
1432                     }
1433                 }
1434             }
1435             if (this.configuration.sipRegisterMode === true)
1436             {
1437                 if (this.sipRegisterState === this.SIP_REGISTERED_STATE)
1438                 {
1439                     this.sipUnregisterPendingFlag = false;
1440                     this.sipRegisterState = this.SIP_UNREGISTERING_STATE;
1441                     if (this.sipRegisterRefreshTimer)
1442                     {
1443                         // Cancel SIP REGISTER refresh timer
1444                         clearTimeout(this.sipRegisterRefreshTimer);
1445                     }
1446                     this.sendNewSipRegisterRequest(0);
1447                 }
1448                 else
1449                 {
1450                     // Refresh SIP REGISTER ongoing, wait the end and excute SIP unregistration
1451                     this.sipUnregisterPendingFlag = true;
1452                 }
1453             }
1454             else
1455             {
1456                 this.reset();
1457                 this.webRTCommClient.onPrivateClientConnectorClosedEvent();
1458             }
1459         }
1460         else
1461         {
1462             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:close(): bad state, unauthorized action");
1463             throw "PrivateJainSipClientConnector:close(): bad state, unauthorized action";
1464         }
1465     }
1466     catch (exception) {
1467         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:close(): catched exception:" + exception);
1468         throw exception;
1469     }
1470 };

1558 /**
1559  * Check configuration 
1560  * @private
1561  * @param {object} configuration SIP user agent configuration
1562  * * <p> Client configuration sample: <br>
1563  * { <br>
1564  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserAgent:"WebRtcCommTestWebApp/0.0.1",<br></span>
1565  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserAgentCapabilities:"+g.oma.sip-im",<br></span>
1566  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipOutboundProxy:"ws://localhost:5082",<br></span>
1567  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipDomain:"sip.net",<br></span>
1568  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserName:"alice",<br></span>
1569  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipLogin:"alice@sip.net,<br></span>
1570  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipPassword:"1234567890",<br></span>
1571  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipUserAgentCapabilities,<br></span>
1572  * <span style="margin-left: 30px">sipRegisterMode:true,<br></span>
1573  * }<br>
1574  *  </p>
1575  * @return true configuration ok false otherwise
1576  */
1577 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.checkConfiguration = function(configuration) {
1578     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration()");
1579     try
1580     {
1581         var check = true;
1582         // sipLogin, sipPassword, sipUserAgentCapabilities not mandatory
1583         if (configuration.sipUserAgent === undefined || configuration.sipUserAgent.length === 0)
1584         {
1585             check = false;
1586             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): missing configuration parameter sipUserAgent");
1587         }
1588 
1589         // stunServer, sipLogin, sipPassword, sipApplicationprofile not mandatory
1590         if (configuration.sipOutboundProxy === undefined || configuration.sipOutboundProxy.length === 0)
1591         {
1592             check = false;
1593             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): missing configuration parameter sipOutboundProxy");
1594         }
1595 
1596         if (configuration.sipDomain === undefined || configuration.sipDomain.length === 0)
1597         {
1598             check = false;
1599             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): missing configuration parameter sipDomain");
1600         }
1601 
1602         if (configuration.sipUserName === undefined || configuration.sipUserName.length === 0)
1603         {
1604             check = false;
1605             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): missing configuration parameter sipUserName");
1606         }
1607 
1608         if (configuration.sipRegisterMode === undefined || configuration.sipRegisterMode.length === 0)
1609         {
1610             check = false;
1611             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): missing configuration parameter sipRegisterMode");
1612         }
1613 
1614         if (configuration.sipLogin !== undefined && configuration.sipLogin === "")
1615         {
1616             configuration.sipLogin = undefined;
1617         }
1618 
1619         if (configuration.sipPassword !== undefined && configuration.sipPassword === "")
1620         {
1621             configuration.sipPassword = undefined;
1622         }
1623 
1624         if (configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities !== undefined && configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities === "")
1625         {
1626             configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities = undefined;
1627         }
1628 
1629         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipUserAgent:" + configuration.sipUserAgent);
1630         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities:" + configuration.sipUserAgentCapabilities);
1631         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipOutboundProxy:" + configuration.sipOutboundProxy);
1632         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipDomain:" + configuration.sipDomain);
1633         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipUserName:" + configuration.sipUserName);
1634         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipLogin:" + configuration.sipLogin);
1635         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipPassword: " + configuration.sipPassword);
1636         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): configuration.sipRegisterMode:" + configuration.sipRegisterMode);
1637         return check;
1638     }
1639     catch (exception) {
1640         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:checkConfiguration(): catched exception:" + exception);
1641         return false;
1642     }

1645 /**
1646  * Implementation of JAIN SIP stack event listener interface: process WebSocket connection event
1647  * @public 
1648  */
1649 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.processConnected = function() {
1650     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processConnected()");
1651     try
1652     {
1653         // Start SIP REGISTER process
1654         if (this.openedFlag === false)
1655         {
1656             if (this.configuration.sipRegisterMode === true)
1657             {
1658                 this.resetSipRegisterContext();
1659                 // Send SIP REGISTER request
1660                 this.sendNewSipRegisterRequest(this.SIP_SESSION_EXPIRATION_TIMER);
1661                 this.sipRegisterState = this.SIP_REGISTERING_STATE;
1662                 return;
1663             }
1664             else
1665             {
1666                 this.openedFlag = true;
1667                 this.webRTCommClient.onPrivateClientConnectorOpenedEvent();
1668                 return;
1669             }
1670         }
1671         else
1672         {
1673             console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processConnected(): this.openedFlag==true !");
1674         }
1675 
1676         // Open failed
1677         this.reset();
1678         this.webRTCommClient.onPrivateClientConnectorOpenErrorEvent();
1679     }
1680     catch (exception) {
1681         this.reset();
1682         this.webRTCommClient.onPrivateClientConnectorOpenErrorEvent();
1683         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processConnected(): catched exception:" + exception);
1684     }
1685 };

1688 /**
1689  * Send SIP REGISTER request 
1690  * @param {int} expiration
1691  * @private
1692  */
1693 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.sendNewSipRegisterRequest = function(expiration) {
1694     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:sendNewSipRegisterRequest()");
1695     var fromSipUriString = this.configuration.sipUserName + "@" + this.configuration.sipDomain;
1696     var jainSipCseqHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createCSeqHeader(1, "REGISTER");
1697     var jainSipCallIdHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createCallIdHeader(new String(new Date().getTime()));
1698     var jainSipExpiresHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createExpiresHeader(expiration);
1699     var jainSipMaxForwardHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createMaxForwardsHeader(70);
1700     var jainSipRequestUri = this.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, this.configuration.sipDomain);
1701     var jainSipAllowListHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createHeaders(PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.SIP_ALLOW_HEADER);
1702     var jainSipFromUri = this.jainSipAddressFactory.createSipURI_user_host(null, fromSipUriString);
1703     var jainSipFromAddress = this.jainSipAddressFactory.createAddress_name_uri(null, jainSipFromUri);
1704     var random = new Date();
1705     var tag = random.getTime();
1706     var jainSipFromHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createFromHeader(jainSipFromAddress, tag);
1707     var jainSipToHeader = this.jainSipHeaderFactory.createToHeader(jainSipFromAddress, null);
1708     var jainSipViaHeader = this.jainSipListeningPoint.getViaHeader();
1709     this.jainSipRegisterRequest = this.jainSipMessageFactory.createRequest(jainSipRequestUri, "REGISTER", jainSipCallIdHeader, jainSipCseqHeader, jainSipFromHeader, jainSipToHeader, jainSipViaHeader, jainSipMaxForwardHeader);
1710     this.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipRegisterRequest, jainSipExpiresHeader);
1711     this.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipRegisterRequest, jainSipAllowListHeader);
1712     this.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipRegisterRequest, this.jainSipContactHeader);
1713 
1714     this.jainSipRegisterTransaction = this.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(this.jainSipRegisterRequest);
1715     this.jainSipRegisterDialog = this.jainSipRegisterTransaction.getDialog();
1716     this.jainSipRegisterRequest.setTransaction(this.jainSipRegisterTransaction);
1717     this.jainSipRegisterTransaction.sendRequest();
1718 };
1719 
1720 /**
1721  * Send Authentitated SIP REGISTER request 
1722  * @param {AuthorizationHeader} jainSipAuthorizationHeader
1723  * @private
1724  */
1725 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.sendAuthenticatedSipRegisterRequest = function(jainSipAuthorizationHeader) {
1726     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:sendAuthenticatedSipRegisterRequest()");
1727     this.jainSipRegisterRequest.removeHeader("Authorization");
1728     var newJainSipRegisterRequest = new SIPRequest();
1729     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setMethod(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getMethod());
1730     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setRequestURI(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getRequestURI());
1731     var headerList = this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getHeaders();
1732     for (var i = 0; i < headerList.length; i++)
1733     {
1734         newJainSipRegisterRequest.addHeader(headerList[i]);
1735     }
1736 
1737     var num = new Number(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getCSeq().getSeqNumber());
1738     newJainSipRegisterRequest.getCSeq().setSeqNumber(num + 1);
1739     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setCallId(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getCallId());
1740     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setVia(this.jainSipListeningPoint.getViaHeader());
1741     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setFrom(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getFrom());
1742     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setTo(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getTo());
1743     newJainSipRegisterRequest.setMaxForwards(this.jainSipRegisterRequest.getMaxForwards());
1744 
1745     this.jainSipRegisterRequest = newJainSipRegisterRequest;
1746     this.jainSipMessageFactory.addHeader(this.jainSipRegisterRequest, jainSipAuthorizationHeader);
1747     this.jainSipRegisterTransaction = this.jainSipProvider.getNewClientTransaction(this.jainSipRegisterRequest);
1748     this.jainSipRegisterRequest.setTransaction(this.jainSipRegisterTransaction);
1749     this.jainSipRegisterTransaction.sendRequest();
1750 };

1785 /**
1786  * Implementation of JAIN SIP stack event listener interface: process SIP request event
1787  * @public 
1788  * @param {RequestEvent} requestEvent JAIN SIP request event
1789  */
1790 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.processRequest = function(requestEvent) {
1791     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processRequest()");
1792     try
1793     {
1794         var jainSipRequest = requestEvent.getRequest();
1795         console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processRequest():jainSipRequest.getCallId().getCallId()="+jainSipRequest.getCallId().getCallId());
1796         var jainSipRequestMethod = jainSipRequest.getMethod();
1797         if (jainSipRequestMethod === "OPTIONS")
1798         {
1799             this.processSipOptionRequest(requestEvent);
1800         }
1801         else
1802         {
1803             // Find related PrivateJainSipCallConnector (subsequent request)
1804             var sipSessionId = jainSipRequest.getCallId().getCallId();
1805             var sessionConnector = this.sessionConnectors[sipSessionId];
1806             if (sessionConnector)
1807             {
1808                 sessionConnector.onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent(requestEvent);
1809             }
1810             else
1811             {
1812                 if (jainSipRequestMethod === "INVITE")
1813                 {
1814                     // Incoming SIP INVITE
1815                     var newWebRTCommCall = new WebRTCommCall(this.webRTCommClient);
1816                     newWebRTCommCall.incomingCallFlag = true;
1817                     newWebRTCommCall.connector = this.createPrivateSessionConnector(newWebRTCommCall, sipSessionId);
1818                     newWebRTCommCall.id = newWebRTCommCall.connector.getId();
1819                     newWebRTCommCall.connector.sipCallState = PrivateJainSipCallConnector.prototype.SIP_INVITED_INITIAL_STATE;
1820                     newWebRTCommCall.connector.onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent(requestEvent);
1821                 }
1822                 else if (jainSipRequestMethod === "MESSAGE")
1823                 {
1824                     // Incoming SIP MESSAGE
1825                     // Find WebRTCommCall linked with the message (if exist)
1826                     var targetedWebRTCommCall = undefined;
1827                     var from = requestEvent.getRequest().getHeader("From").getAddress().getURI().getUser();
1828                     for (var sipCallId in this.sessionConnectors)
1829                     {
1830                         var sessionConnector = this.sessionConnectors[sipCallId];
1831                         if (sessionConnector instanceof PrivateJainSipCallConnector)
1832                         {
1833                             if (sessionConnector.isOpened())
1834                             {
1835                                 if (sessionConnector.webRTCommCall.isIncoming() && sessionConnector.webRTCommCall.callerPhoneNumber === from)
1836                                 {
1837                                     targetedWebRTCommCall = sessionConnector.webRTCommCall;
1838                                     break;
1839                                 }
1840                                 else if (sessionConnector.webRTCommCall.calleePhoneNumber === from)
1841                                 {
1842                                     targetedWebRTCommCall = sessionConnector.webRTCommCall;
1843                                     break;
1844                                 }
1845                             }
1846                         }
1847                     }
1848 
1849                     // Build WebRTCommMessage
1850                     var newWebRTCommMessage = new WebRTCommMessage(this.webRTCommClient, targetedWebRTCommCall);
1851                     newWebRTCommMessage.connector.onJainSipClientConnectorSipRequestEvent(requestEvent);
1852                 }
1853                 else
1854                 {
1855                     console.warn("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processRequest(): SIP request ignored");
1856                     //@todo Should send SIP response 404 NOT FOUND or 501 NOT_IMPLEMENTED 				 
1857                 }
1858 
1859             }
1860         }
1861     }
1862     catch (exception) {
1863         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:processRequest(): catched exception:" + exception);
1864     }
1865 };

1960 /**
1961  * SIP REGISTER refresh timeout
1962  * @private 
1963  */
1964 PrivateJainSipClientConnector.prototype.onSipRegisterTimeout = function() {
1965     console.debug("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onSipRegisterTimeout()");
1966     try
1967     {
1968         if (this.sipRegisterState === this.SIP_REGISTERED_STATE)
1969         {
1970             this.sipRegisterRefreshTimer = undefined;
1971             this.sipRegisterState = this.SIP_REGISTER_REFRESHING_STATE;
1972             // Send SIP REGISTER request
1973             this.sendNewSipRegisterRequest(this.SIP_SESSION_EXPIRATION_TIMER);
1974         }
1975         else
1976         {
1977             console.warn("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onSipRegisterTimeout(): SIP REGISTER refresh stopped");
1978         }
1979     }
1980     catch (exception) {
1981         console.error("PrivateJainSipClientConnector:onSipRegisterTimeout(): catched exception:" + exception);
1982     }
1983 };
